    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was looking at some old photos today... it's weird. i don't even recognize that person anymore. not just the face, but the whole spirit of it. it feels like the real me actually died a long time ago, maybe 20 years back. now i'm just... going through the motions. like a ghost or a shell of what i was supposed to be. just a walking corpse.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
